  "remarks": "\n The Dalzavod Ship Repair Centre JSC is an involved person under the Russia (EU) (Sanctions) Regulations 2019 as it is involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian defence sector. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
